<item>
            <title>[LU-889] rework extent_recovery_timer()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-889</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is an issue with current implementation of extend_recovery_timer() where the timeout calculation is wrong if we want to extend timeout value by a client estimate. This issue was imported by commit: 8da33c6cc5192303fcd18f45892e1f115004e662.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this task, I&apos;m going to restore the code to 2.1 release.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
